result.title: lee me alon
result.content:
please lee me alon, i just want to be left alon. do not botha me, i just want to be left alon. i tell you 'lee me alon' and you still bother me?? why u do dis? every morneen i put cocoa butta on my skin, so that my skin has the healthy glo. now lee me alon. i dont wan dis. you try to give me dis, i don wan dis. i want to be left alone.

eveyr morneen i wake up, i go outside. de first morneen, i find a snake and i kill de snake. de second morneen, i go outside. anotha snake. de same color, de same size. i kill da snake.

the third morning. de turd morneen, i go outside, there is a snake and right before i kill de snake, de snake looks up at me and he says to me 'i just want to be left alon, why you do dis?' i left the snake alon.

i find no more snakes in the morneen.
